SYSTEMS SHOULD BE CONCISE - It should be simple, lean, clear, easy and functional.
SYSTEMS SHOULD BE S.O.L.I.D. - It should respect the SOLID principles.
SYSTEMS SHOULD BE S.M.A.R.T. - It should follow the SMART framework.
SYSTEMS SHOULD BE HELPFUL - It should be self documenting and well documented.
SYSTEMS SHOULD BE HUMANE - Systems are made by humans and for everyone.
